body_text = "[color=firebrick]The Pit[/color] is a dangerous tile. Units that got pushed into it is removed from the battle immediately.

You cannot directly step on it, but you can use different skills and attacks to push enemies into [color=firebrick]the Pit[/color]

If an enemy has a very high health, consider pushing them into [color=firebrick]the Pit[/color]

